div.p:
The Inspector of Army Schools is expec'ed to arrive at Alexandria on the
                            15th inst. The order of inspections will be as follows:- Alexandria;
                            Abbassia; Khartoum (probably); other schools in Cairo.

General Sir F. Lugard, High Commissioner of North Nigeria, who is at
                            present in England, has resigned owing to ill-health and will not
                            return. (Peuter)
